---
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import '../../styles/howto.css'
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>lain.art — How‑To</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  </head>

  <body>
    <Header />

    <main>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <h2>1. Create</h2>
          <p>Produce original works of art about <strong>Lain</strong> where she is clearly visible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <h2>2. Authenticate</h2>
          <p>Log in securely using your <strong>Internet Identity</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <h2>3. Submit Fee</h2>
          <p>Pay a small fee in <strong>Laincoin</strong> to process your submission.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <h2>4. Verification</h2>
          <p>Your artwork is checked for authenticity and originality against our database and AI systems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <h2>5. Reward</h2>
          <p>If successful, you’ll receive a reward in <strong>Laincoin</strong> and a custom <strong>NFT</strong> proving ownership of your art.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
